== 播映 ==
1985年9月15日至1986年1月25日，美国广播公司共播出13集《女干探》。<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="AllMovies1" />。试播集本是1985年4月15日播映的[[电视电影|电视电影]]<ref name="AllMovies1" />，后又在九月当成试播节目重新播出<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source5" />。据李·马古利斯（{{lang|en|Lee Margulies}}）在《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》刊登的报导记载，四月的电视电影收视成绩很好<ref name="Source122">{{cite news | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1985-05-09-ca-6992-story.html | title = ABC Pulls Switch On Its Fall Prime-time Lineup | last = Margulies | first = Lee | date = 1985-05-09 | newspaper = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151208170726/http://articles.latimes.com/1985-05-09/entertainment/ca-6992_1_fall-schedule | archivedate = 2015-12-08 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-08-25 }}</ref>。电视剧开播后因着重描绘暴力挨批<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source3" />，是[[看門狗新聞學|看门狗组织]]的重点关注对象<ref name="Source2" />。试播集共有18人被杀，制作人甚至承诺将来的节目会死更多人<ref name="News4">{{cite news | title = TV Rose doesn't mind 'Dirty Harriette' label | author = CP | date = 1985-08-14 | newspaper = [[环球邮报|The Globe and Mail]] | url = https://www.nexis.com/docview/getDocForCuiReq?lni=4MT7-22X0-TXJ2-N036&csi=280434&oc=00240&perma=true | via = [[律商联讯|Nexis]] | accessdate = 2020-08-25 | archive-date = 2018-06-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180616103456/https://www.nexis.com/docview/getDocForCuiReq?lni=4MT7-22X0-TXJ2-N036&csi=280434&oc=00240&perma=true | dead-url = no }}{{subscription required}}</ref>。播出期间，全国电视暴力联盟（{{lang|en|The National Coalition on Television Violence}}）谴责这是电视上“最暴力的节目”<ref name="Book5">{{cite book | last = O'Dell | first = Cary | title = June Cleaver Was a Feminist!: Reconsidering the Female Characters of Early Television | year = 2013 | publisher = McFarland | location = Jefferson | isbn = 978-0-7864-7177-5 | ref = ODell2013 | page = 143}}</ref>。罗斯对此辩称《女干探》无意据实描绘警察，更像发生在英雄奇迹世界的故事，马奥尼就像[[超级英雄|超级英雄]]<ref name="News3">{{cite news | title = Is Lady Blue 'Dirty Harriet'? You bet it is | last = Davis | first = Ivor | date = 1985-09-14 | newspaper = [[环球邮报|The Globe and Mail]] | url = https://www.nexis.com/docview/getDocForCuiReq?lni=4MT7-22M0-TXJ2-N1N4&csi=280434&oc=00240&perma=true | via = [[律商联讯|Nexis]] | accessdate = 2020-08-25 | archive-date = 2018-06-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180616103800/https://www.nexis.com/docview/getDocForCuiReq?lni=4MT7-22M0-TXJ2-N1N4&csi=280434&oc=00240&perma=true | dead-url = no }}{{subscription required}}</ref>。

《女干探》起初占据[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]周四晚八点档，在同时段节目中收视排名第三，仅次于半小时[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]《[[歡樂酒店|歡樂酒店]]》和《[[夜间法庭|夜间法庭]]》（''{{lang|en|Night Court}}''），以及侦破剧《[[西蒙兄弟|西蒙兄弟]]》（''{{lang|en|Simon & Simon}}''）<ref name="Source3" />。播出七集后，节目播出时间后移到九点，为《[[浮华世家|浮华世家]]》（''{{lang|en|The Colbys}}''）让路<ref name="Source3" /><ref name="Source122" />。美国广播公司一度宣布续订《女干探》，声称会改在每周的另一天播出，如果收视率理想就每周都会播映<ref name="Source122" />。节目后来改为周六晚九点档，需同《[[黃金女郎|黃金女郎]]》竞争<ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source9">{{cite journal | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=8ckBAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA157&dq=%22Lady+Blue%22+%22ABC%22&hl=en&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22Lady%20Blue%22%20%22ABC%22&f=false | title = Double Fantasy | last = Leonard | first = John | date = 1985-12-02 | journal = [[紐約_(雜誌)|New York]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180112232918/https://books.google.com/books?id=8ckBAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA157&dq=%22Lady+Blue%22+%22ABC%22&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjdq9DqxtPYAhUsY98KHeNuAt44FBDoAQhPMAg#v=onepage&q=%22Lady%20Blue%22%20%22ABC%22&f=false | archivedate = 2018-01-12 | deadurl = no | page = 157 | access-date = 2020-08-25 }}</ref>，但过分暴力的投诉如影随形<ref name="Source9" />。

美国广播公司于1986年初停播《女干探》<ref name="Book1" /><ref name="Source7">{{cite journal | url = https://people.com/archive/snagging-a-steady-job-on-tv-turns-out-to-be-a-real-thorn-in-jamie-roses-side-vol-26-no-23/ | title = Snagging a Steady Job on TV Turns Out to Be a Real Thorn in Jamie Rose's Side | last = Grant | first = James | date = 1986-12-08 | journal = [[人物_(雜誌)|People]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200320051954/https://people.com/archive/snagging-a-steady-job-on-tv-turns-out-to-be-a-real-thorn-in-jamie-roses-side-vol-26-no-23/ | archivedate = 2020-03-20 | deadurl = no | access-date = 2020-08-25 }}</ref>，里斯曼认为收视成绩不理想也是节目取消的重要原因<ref name="Source1" />。罗斯事后表示：“无论如何，这都是很棒的经历。人这辈子能主演电视剧的机会可不多，特别是女人”<ref name="Source7" />。{{lang|en|[[Lifetime|Lifetime]]}}电视台后来重播《女干探》，该台主要面向女观众，所播电视剧一向涉及以传统男子岗位为职业的女角色，如《[[维罗妮卡·克莱尔|维罗妮卡·克莱尔]]》（''{{lang|en|Veronica Clare}}''）和《[[共犯_(美国电视剧)|共犯]]》（{{lang|en|''Partners in Crime''}}）中的女私家侦探，以及《[[凯·奥布莱恩|凯·奥布莱恩]]》（{{lang|en|''Kay O'Brien''}}）中的女医师<ref name="Book10">{{cite book | last1 = Dines | first1 = Gail | last2 = Humez | first2 = Jean M. | title = Gender, Race, and Class in Media: A Text-Reader | year = 2003 | publisher = Sage | location = Thousand Oaks | isbn = 0-7619-2260-1 | page = 620 | accessdate = 2020-08-25 | ref = DinesHumez2003 |url = https://archive.org/details/genderraceclassi0000unse}}{{subscription required}}</ref>。本剧至今没有发布[[数码多功能影音光盘|数码多功能影音光盘]]、[[蓝光光盘|蓝光光盘]]或[[流媒体|流媒体]]<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source13">{{cite web | url = http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/shows/Lady-Blue/2648 | title = Lady Blue (1985) | publisher = TVShowsOnDVD.com | archivedate = 2015-10-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151024063045/http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/shows/Lady-Blue/2648 | access-date = 2020-08-25 }}</ref>，版权归[[米高梅|米高梅]]所有，但暂无家用媒体发行计划<ref name="Source1" />。

== 专业评价 ==
《女干探》播出期间，大部分评论批评剧中过分强调暴力<ref name="AllMovies1" /><ref name="Book5" />。奥康纳认为剧中暴力过于盲目，执法手段引人质疑<ref name="Source2" />，安德森认为节目本来颇具潜力<ref name="Source3" />：“如果能多播几季，杰米·罗斯可能成为大明星”<ref name="Source3" />。戴维·英曼（{{lang|en|David Inman}}）1991年的著作《电视百科全书》声称，即便美国广播公司播过的愚蠢节目不可胜数，但《女干探》依旧名列前茅<ref>{{cite book | last = Inman | first = David | title = The TV Encyclopedia | year = 1991 | publisher = Perigee | location = New York | isbn = 0-399-51704-9 | ref = Inman1991 | accessdate = 2020-08-25 | url = https://archive.org/details/tvencyclopedia0000inma | page = 683}}</ref>。《华盛顿邮报》刊登劳埃德·格罗夫（{{lang|en|Lloyd Grove}}）的评论，认为《女干探》本是很好看的快节奏节目，但对暴力的过分依赖不但喧宾夺主，而且令人厌恶，他还批评编剧罗伯特·文森特·奥尼尔（{{lang|en|Robert Vincent O'Neill}}）剽窃伊斯特伍德主演电影和1971年影片《[[霹靂神探|法国贩毒网]]》的构思。<ref name="News5" />。里斯曼认为电视剧虽然评价欠佳，但青少年观众，特别是男观众应该会喜欢马奥尼的外貌和态度<ref name="Source1" />。

电视研究学者卡里·奥德尔（{{lang|en|Cary O'Dell}}）2013年的著作《琼·克里弗是女权主义者！：重新审视早期电视中的女角色》（{{lang|en|''June Cleaver Was a Feminist!: Reconsidering the Female Characters of Early Television''}}）认为，《女干探》是幻想“女子主导硬汉警察体裁电视剧”的“有趣实验”。在他看来，无论马奥尼遇到的批评还是节目那么快停播，归根究底都源自[[性别歧视主义|性别歧视]]，不过是当时的社会还不能接受女人“如此叛逆、蔑视权威并采用残忍手段（办案）”。奥德尔称赞《女干探》领先于时代，针对马奥尼的负面评价与1991年电影《[[塞尔玛与路易丝|塞尔玛与路易丝]]》两位女主角赢得的一片赞誉对比显著。<ref name="Book5" />

